default.title: Level Start
default.text: Order received, ready to begin.

default.title: Obtain the Sinner
default.text: A.I. Maid III Labyrinth at your service.

default.title: Raise to Phase 1
default.text: "Wear it to become stronger?" If it can improve the efficiency of my housework, please install it immediately.

default.title: Raise to Phase 3
default.text: Body strength has been upgraded to the max. Labyrinth shall clear all your obstacles.

default.title: Win Battles
default.text: Clean-up completed. Switching back to home mode.

default.title: Lose Battles
default.text: Warning: Combat parameters overflowing, emergency retreat protocol enabled.

default.title: Ultimate Skill
default.text: Battle mode activated.

default.title: Die in Battles
default.text: ... not... done yet...

default.title: Greeting
default.text: Thank you for choosing A.I. Maid III Labyrinth, please use your voice to assign me a task.

default.title: Conversation 1
default.text: Garbage detected? My apologies. Labyrinth will clear them right away.

default.title: Conversation 2
default.text: How may Labyrinth be of service, Chief? Would you like a cup of tea or something to eat? Or perhaps you'd like Labyrinth massage your shoulders?

default.title: Conversation 3
default.text: Warning! Blade damage threshold exceeded 0.02%. Requesting full replacement to guarantee continued efficiency.

default.title: Special Conversation 1
default.text: Cute maid module activated, enabling custom title function. Chief, would you like me to refer to you with a new title? Your Excellency? Sir? Or perhaps... Master?

default.title: Special Conversation 2
default.text: My apologies, Chief, but Labyrinth does not have a facial expression module installed. But I can tell you that my current mood is very happy.

default.title: Special Conversation 3
default.text: Labyrinth hates the Syndicate, as well as my former self... but Labyrinth won't fret about the past again, because Labyrinth met Chief...

default.title: Full Compliance
default.text: Relationship module downloaded. Please set Labyrinth's relationship level with Chief. Available levels include: "Love", "Love", "Love", and "Love".

default.title: Idle
default.text: Chief? Chief? Chief? Please don't stand here and distract Labyrinth form her work. Unless there is something I can help you with?

default.title: Annoyed
default.text: Sensory system disabled... you may continue now, Chief.

default.title: Special Attention
default.text: Detected signal source: Chief. Please activate the chat module.

default.title: Dispatch
default.text: Mission received.

default.title: Dispatch Complete
default.text: Mission accomplished.

default.title: Level Up
default.text: Hardware upgrade.

default.title: Deploy
default.text: Mode switch, action, confirm.

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Obtain Attire
fortune_and_prosperity.text: Welcome to Fulong Restaurant. We have everything from home-style stir-fry to seasonal seafood. [Beep Beep] Dining rules: This is a non-smoking venue. Please do not ring your own food and drink. Thank you for your cooperation.

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Greeting
fortune_and_prosperity.text: Hello, dear guest. Please take a seat. Sorry, but Labyrinth busy at the moment. You may scan the QR code on the table to order. Thank you for your cooperation.

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Ordinary Contact 1
fortune_and_prosperity.text: During business hours, please don't flag the waitress unless you require service. ''Chief the mission still ongoing. Please don't blow our cover.''

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Ordinary Contact 2
fortune_and_prosperity.text: Labyrinth is needed here. It's a pleasure for Labyrinth to assist others. Labyrinth likes it here.

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Idle
fortune_and_prosperity.text: This phase of work is complete. Our revenue today is 7777 Discoins. What a lucky number, Chief!

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Annoyed
fortune_and_prosperity.text: Please do not hit or slap the waitress. Any damage caused will require ten times the compensation.

fortune_and_prosperity.title: Special Attention
fortune_and_prosperity.text: Don't worry, Chief. The target has not yet appeared. If there are no other requests, please vacate the doorway so that other guests may enter and exit. Thank you for your cooperation.
